{"data":[{"id":563874876,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"03476b0bf9c8a176d0da6d76ab649f85","url_token":"zhi-bi-quan-shi-yz","name":"执笔诠释yz","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/03476b0bf9c8a176d0da6d76ab649f85","user_type":"people","headline":"大一学生，开始掉头发，准备架网","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":1,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563874876","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546306160,"updated_time":1546306160,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":5,"comment_count":1,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e说实话，我也就是一个大一学生，大学元旦要放假，不然我何苦咸吃萝卜淡操心等00:00看这个证明(这个可以作为论点一)\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e要是我还是一个苦逼的高中生，我才懒得管你发不发证明过程，要是你能证得出来，我也不看你的知乎，那时知乎热榜 微博热搜甚至各大头条肯定炸掉(高中生花几分钟阅览这些不浪费时间)，结果今年的热搜关注点都在跨年晚会，热榜关注于那场烂电影，我也就明白了这一切。(作为论点一补充)\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e因为深深钦佩于华罗庚先生 王元先生 陈景润先生等中国伟大数学家对哥猜的研究，以及自身对哥猜 黎曼猜想 等这些问题能够被解决充满期待，故等到那一刻，结果很失望(可以作为论点二)\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我对一个高中生对这些问题有兴趣有尝试的想法，不管他是不是在营销，我都抱有一丝丝幻想，谁不希望自己的国家诞生一个超级天才(可以作为论点三)，可是仅有的那点希望也变成了失望。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e总结一下，00:00那刻我的舍友惊呼的不是“新年快乐”，而是“快看他有没有证出来”，当然一个宿舍的人都很失望，看到开头就放弃看下去的欲望。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e综上，我还是太闲了~\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"说实话，我也就是一个大一学生，大学元旦要放假，不然我何苦咸吃萝卜淡操心等00:00看这个证明(这个可以作为论点一)要是我还是一个苦逼的高中生，我才懒得管你发不发证明过程，要是你能证得出来，我也不看你的知乎，那时知乎热榜 微博热搜甚至各大头条肯定炸…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=362\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=360\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","totals":254